Package: Rtts
Type: Package
Title: Convert Text into Speech
Depends: RCurl
Version: 0.2.5
Date: 2015-05-26
Author: Xiaodong Deng
Maintainer: Xiaodong Deng <xd_deng@hotmail.com>
Description: Convert text into speech (voice file in .mp3 format) with API offered by Google Translate. Only English is supported currently.
URL: http://r-text-2-speech.r-forge.r-project.org/
License: GPL-3
LazyData: TRUE
